{"tid":2500303,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登主持視像氣候峰會　呼籲各國要即時採取行動","createTime":"2021-04-22T13:38:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-22T13:42:29.000Z","uid":295230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"6893252db5f2a96628bdb9febad94388e72fa86c","tid":2500303,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:38:50.000Z","msg":"美國總統拜登，今明兩日在白宮主持及召開全球氣候變化領袖視像峰會，峰會邀請40多個國家及國際組織領袖出席。<br />\n<br />\n拜登在發言時，呼籲各國要即時採取行動，將今次峰會視為第一步，認為全球都要應對氣候變化，除了國家層面之外，企業及個人都有責任。拜登表示，美國佔全球排放量的一成半，美國將收緊溫室氣體的排放，承諾到10年後，將排放量較2005年少百分之五十，到2050年達致零排放。"},{"pid":"eaeadce835a5a0c193716300a72598e863e575d2","tid":2500303,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:38:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1587206-20210422.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1587206-20210422.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=0rs6uxY5NhpkL%2Fcp6PdBrRURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=5afe17f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1587206-20210422.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=d24f9088\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1587206-20210422.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"37e9065b1e15b719dd5d0531679dbaf6bf422707","tid":2500303,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:39:22.000Z","msg":"你再開po咁密就唔follow<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"978603a5b4c5f7eb6020f44378b2bf9cd9921d29","tid":2500303,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37e9065b1e15b719dd5d0531679dbaf6bf422707","tid":2500303,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:39:22.000Z","msg":"你再開po咁密就唔follow<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-22T13:39:39.000Z","msg":"好<img src=\"/asse